Peter Boneparth Biography

Peter Boneparth has been a Senior Advisor at Irving Capital Partners, a private equity group, since February 2009. He is also on the Board of Directors for both JetBlue Airways and Kohls. Peter is the former President and Chief Executive Officer of Jones Apparel Group, a leading designer and ...
>>Read More 


Peter Boneparth has been a Senior Advisor at Irving Capital Partners, a
private equity group, since February 2009. He is also on the Board of
Directors for both JetBlue Airways and Kohls. Peter is the former
President and Chief Executive Officer of Jones Apparel Group, a leading
designer and marketer of apparel and footwear brands. Before becoming
involved with the Jones Apparel Group, Mr. Boneparth spent 10 years in
the investment banking field and also practiced law.

