Insider Activity


Individual




Peter Boneparth



Mr. Peter Boneparth is Senior Advisor at Irving Place Capital Management LP and Independent Director at JetBlue Airways Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at JetBlue Airways Corp. and Kohl's Corp.
Prior to joining Irving Place Capital in 2009, Mr. Boneparth served most recently as Chief Executive Officer of Jones Apparel Group., a leading designer and marketer of apparel and footwear brands. During his time at Jones Apparel, he expanded the designer‚Äôs apparel offerings and grew the company through the acquisitions of Maxwell Shoe Company, Gloria Vanderbilt, Barneys New York, Kasper/Anne Klein, and L.E.I.  Previously, he served as Chief Executive Officer of Jones Moderate Division and also was Chief Executive Officer, President of McNaughton Apparel Group.
Mr. Boneparth holds J.D. from the University of Virginia and B.S. degree, Phi Beta Kappa, from the University of North Carolina.



