Mr. Boneparth and the board have disagreed over the company‚Äôs future for quite some time, and the board decided in March not to renew Mr. Boneparth‚Äôs contract when it expired in 2009. At that time, the board granted him 74,000 additional shares of restricted stock. Continue reading the main story







